docs Print
    Terminal output sink for the unit converter.
    Prints the formatted conversion result to the terminal.
done

sink Print
    take text as text
    emit result as bool
    fail error as text
body
    _ = term.print(text)
    ok = true
    emit ok
done

test Print
    r = Print("100 km = 62.1371 mi")
    must r == true
done
